<i>verb</i>: 에돌다 [에ː돌다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>에돌다 [에ː돌다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. make a detour; take a roundabout way</dd><br>
<dd>곧장 나아가지 않고 멀리 돌다.</dd><br>
<dd>To take a long way, not going by the shortest route.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hang around; hover</dd><br>
<dd>한 곳에 머물지 않고 이리저리 빙빙 돌다.</dd><br>
<dd>To circle round, not staying in one place.</dd><br>
<dd>3. speak in a roundabout way; euphemize</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글을 곧바로 하지 않고 빙빙 돌리다.</dd><br>
<dd>To talk in a roundabout way without saying or writing directly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>